                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ".github/workflows/ with Gate 1 (schema validation), Gate 2 (injection probes), Gate 3 (regression eval), Gate 4 (canary monitoring), the weekly scorecard job, and the architecture drift detection check — all configured and ready to run on the first commit."
