          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "All variants share the same directory structure and the same CI pipeline skeleton. The differences are in the source code entry point (handler.py vs handler.ts vs lambda_handler.py) and the default values in the prompt template (e.g., the batch variant sets max_input_tokens to 50000 rather than 8000 because batch processing operates on larger inputs)."
